# Components

All components live in `src/components/`. They read from the Zustand store via `useGraphStore` and dispatch mutations through store methods — no local state for graph data.

## Responsibilities

| Component             | Role                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
| --------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `GraphCanvas`         | React Flow canvas. Wires `nodeTypes`, `edgeTypes`, `connectionLineComponent` (`NessoConnectionLine`), store change handlers. Respects inset props; `onMoveEnd` saves viewport to the store (`saveViewport`). Optional `onViewportZoomChange` drives the bottom-dock zoom `%` (wheel, +/-, fit, graph switch).                |
| `ConceptNode`         | Custom node. Renders text, confidence dots, reviewed badge. Inline rename: measuring span holds width, transparent input overlays while editing; underline hidden during edit. Handles click → `setSelected`. Handle ids `out` / `in` (`conceptHandles.ts`) so `ConnectionMode.Loose` resolves the handle under the pointer. |
| `NessoConnectionLine` | Custom connection preview while dragging a new edge: same quadratic geometry as `NessoEdge`, starts at the handle under the cursor (left vs right).                                                                                                                                                                          |
| `NessoEdge`           | Custom edge. Draws line with style (solid/dashed/dotted/double/wavy) and end glyph based on `EdgeTypeDef`. Respects `edgeEncoding` setting.                                                                                                                                                                                  |
| `GlyphSVG`            | Pure SVG renderer for the 16 `GlyphKind` icons used on edges.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
| `TopBar`              | Top chrome: centered pill (brand, `GraphSwitcher`, search placeholder ⌘K); absolute top-right pill (`GraphIO` export/import, relation-types lines icon, review **R**, theme, shortcuts **?**, settings gear **⌘,**).                                                                                                            |
| `GraphSwitcher`       | Dropdown attached to the graph title in `TopBar`. Switches between graphs, creates new ones, and renames the current graph via inline edit (double-click).                                                                                                                                                                   |
| `GraphIO`             | Top-bar control: dropdown to export current graph as JSON download or import a JSON file into a new graph (`importGraph`).                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
| `BottomDock`          | Fixed bottom dock. Fit/center graph, zoom in/out/percent label, **+ concept**.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
| `RelationTypesDialog` | Centered modal (same shell as `ShortcutsDialog` / `SettingsDialog`). Relation-type reference; opened from TopBar; backdrop / Escape closes via `App`.                                                                                                                                                                        |
| `Inspector`           | Left panel. Appears when a node or edge is selected. Edits `text`, `conf` for nodes; `type` for edges via type chips.                                                                                                                                                                                              |
| `RelationPicker`      | Dropdown grid for selecting an `EdgeTypeName`. Groups by `EdgeCategory`.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
| `MentorBubble`        | FAB + card. Socratic AI chat; card expanded state is `mentorPanelExpanded` on the store (persisted). See `mentor.mdc`.                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
| `SocratesGlyph`       | SVG avatar for Socrates (used in `MentorBubble`).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
| `ReviewMode`          | Full-screen overlay. Walks through low-confidence or stale nodes for spaced-repetition review.                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
| `ShortcutsDialog`     | Overlay listing keyboard shortcuts (? / toolbar). Closes on backdrop click or Escape (wired from `App`).                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
| `SettingsDialog`      | Overlay for AI: **`aiMode`** toggle (**Remote API** vs **Local model** / WebLLM download progress). Remote branch: `aiBaseUrl`, `aiModel`, `aiApiKey`. Gear / **⌘,**. Same backdrop pattern as `ShortcutsDialog`.                                                                                                                                                                                              |
| `Onboarding`          | First-run overlay explaining the core workflow.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |

## Layout

`App.tsx` renders all panels over a single `position: fixed; inset: 0` root. `GraphCanvas` receives inset props so the React Flow viewport avoids panel overlap — panels do not clip the canvas, they just narrow the usable area. `leftInset` widens when the `Inspector` is visible; relation types are a modal, not an inset panel.

## No prop drilling

Components read global state directly from `useGraphStore`. Do not add props for data that is already in the store — add a selector instead.
